title: CS Crosses Above Key Moving Average Level - Nasdaq.com
text: In trading on Thursday, shares of Credit Suisse Group AG (Symbol: CS) crossed above their 200 day moving average of $11.90, changing hands as high as $12.26 per share. Credit Suisse Group AG shares are currently trading up about 3.1% on the day. The chart below shows the one year performance of CS shares, versus its 200 day moving average:     Looking at the chart above, CS's low point in its 52 week range is $10.23 per share, with $15.99 as the 52 week high point - that compares with a last trade of $12.23.
